title: Presidential Nomination Sent to the Senate, 12/8/09 | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House
Office of the Press Secretary


For Immediate Release
December 08, 2009

 



Presidential Nomination Sent to the Senate, 12/8/09




Michael Peter Huerta, of the District of Columbia, to be Deputy Administrator of the Federal Aviation Administration, vice Robert A. Sturgell, resigned.
